# Model access for the research agent — copy to `.env` only if you need a fallback.
#
# DEFAULT (recommended): leave everything unset. The agent uses claude-agent-sdk,
# which runs on your logged-in Claude Code session (e.g. a Claude Max subscription)
# with ZERO API keys. Just run `claude` once to log in, then run the agent.
#
# FALLBACK A — Anthropic API key (for a reviewer without a Claude Code login):
# ANTHROPIC_API_KEY=sk-ant-...
#
# FALLBACK B — Anthropic-compatible endpoint (e.g. Z.AI / GLM):
# ANTHROPIC_BASE_URL=https://api.z.ai/api/anthropic
# ANTHROPIC_AUTH_TOKEN=your-token-here
#
# No code change is needed for any path: the SDK inherits whatever the Claude Code
# session / environment is configured to use.
